This project is on realtime parking system.

A.There are two apk files one is for user(who wants to park) and another is for admin(the one who is at the parking side)
note:install both apks on two different devices
how to use:

User side:(app is based on firebase)

1.The user side app name is parkit.
2.AS you get sign in(this login is based on firebase) on home page you get the help button....here you find a video to how to use it.

Admin side:(app is static)

1.The admin side apk name is Admin.
2.As you get login(username: password:) to add user click on button #adduser and similarly click on #enduser while user leave parking
3.As you click on end user it will generate bill show charges.   
